data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. In the Winter springs neighborhood, tucked away in the cul-de-sac  a 3 bed 2 bath POOL home is ready for you! This newly painted open floor plan home features a newer roof (2019) new carpet in the bedrooms , nest thermostat with security cameras. Wood burning fire place in the large family room which is surround sound wired and ready for entertaining. Convenient location, near shopping, parks, and major highways, this home is ready for you to make it your own!
